To kick off the new year, MultiChoice Nigeria recently announced the DStv Step Up offer for both active and disconnected subscribers. It has become a tradition of the leading entertainment and media company to usher in the new year with the offer that allows subscribers to pay less to enjoy an exciting lineup of world-class quality entertainment. With the DStv Step Up offer, customers who upgrade or reconnect to the next higher package, will get a higher boost to enjoy a wide array of content on their upgraded packages within 48 hours of reconnection at no additional cost. “It’s our mission to give the best entertainment to our customers at all times. We see this offer as an opportunity to get our customers to enjoy the great content that is currently available on higher packages for less, thereby giving them something to get excited about this January,” remarked Chief Executive Officer, MultiChoice Nigeria, John Ugbe. The offer is only available to customers on the DStv Yanga, Compact and Compact Plus packages. For GOtv customers on Jinja, Jolli and GOtv Max packages are eligible for this offer.